snippet.title: Smack Studio - Official Release Window Trailer | OTK Games Expo 2024
snippet.description: Check out the latest Smack Studio trailer to see gameplay and how you can create stages and characters in this sandbox platform game with built-in creation tools. Smack Studio will be leaving Early Access in July 2024.
